Package system

Interface Summary
Ambulance The Ambulance interface represents the set of all ambulances known by the system.
AmbulanceChooser This interface represents ambulance chooser module.
Broker The broker interface present an API to add incident information to the database
Communicator The communicator represent the interface used to communicate with the external world.
Coord This interface represents coordinates on the map.
Incident The Incident interface represent the collection of all the incidents stored in the system.
IncidentProcessor This interface represents incident processor module.
Map This interface represents the map of the world known by the system.
Mobilizer This interface represents the mobilizer module.
Resolver This interface represents resolver module that is able to close an incident.
